DataSource.RecordSource: SELECT child.ProductID, child.ProductID as ChildProductID, child.Code, child.Revision, child.Description, 0 as IsParent, ITM_BOM.ProductID as ParentID,(SELECT ( ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(lc.OHQuantity, 0) - ISNULL(lc.CommitQuantity, 0)), 0) - ISNULL((SELECT ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(TH.Quantity,0)),0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory TH INNER JOIN dbo.MST_TranType TT ON TT.TranTypeID = TH.TranTypeID WHERE TT.Type = 1 AND TH.PostDate > '2006-07-01' AND TH.CCNID = lc.CCNID AND TH.MasterLocationID = lc.MasterLocationID AND TH.LocationID = lc.LocationID AND TH.ProductID = lc.ProductID ) ,0) - ISNULL((SELECT ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(TH.Quantity,0)),0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory TH INNER JOIN dbo.MST_TranType TT ON TT.TranTypeID = TH.TranTypeID WHERE TT.Type = 2 AND TH.PostDate > '2006-07-01' AND TH.CCNID = lc.CCNID AND TH.MasterLocationID = lc.MasterLocationID AND TH.LocationID = lc.LocationID AND TH.ProductID = lc.ProductID ) ,0) + ISNULL((SELECT ISNULL(SUM(ISNULL(TH.Quantity,0)),0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory TH INNER JOIN dbo.MST_TranType TT ON TT.TranTypeID = TH.TranTypeID WHERE TT.Type = 0 AND TH.PostDate > '2006-07-01' AND TH.CCNID = lc.CCNID AND TH.MasterLocationID = lc.MasterLocationID AND TH.LocationID = lc.LocationID AND TH.ProductID = lc.ProductID ) ,0) ) FROM IV_LocationCache lc WHERE lc.CCNID = 1 AND lc.LocationID = 154 AND lc.ProductID = child.ProductID GROUP BY lc.ProductID, lc.LocationID, lc.MasterLocationID, lc.CCNID) as BeginStock, ISNULL(ITM_BOM.Quantity, 0) as BOM_Quantity FROM ITM_Product child INNER JOIN ITM_BOM ON ITM_BOM.ComponentID = child.ProductID WHERE ITM_BOM.ProductID IN (SELECT DISTINCT parent.ProductID FROM ITM_Product parent INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderDetail poDetail ON poDetail.ProductID = parent.ProductID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderMaster poMaster ON poMaster.PurchaseOrderMasterID = poDetail.PurchaseOrderMasterID INNER JOIN ITM_Routing ON ITM_Routing.ProductID = parent.ProductID WHERE ITM_Routing.Type = 1 AND poMaster.CCNID = 1 AND Month(poMaster.OrderDate) = 07 AND Year(poMaster.OrderDate) = 2006 AND poMaster.PartyID = 94) ORDER BY child.Code, child.Description

DataSource.RecordSource: SELECT DISTINCT parent.ProductID, 0 as ParentID,307 as ChildProductID, parent.Code, parent.Description, parent.Revision, 1 as IsParent, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code as BuyingUM FROM ITM_Product parent INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderDetail poDetail ON poDetail.ProductID = parent.ProductID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderMaster poMaster ON poMaster.PurchaseOrderMasterID = poDetail.PurchaseOrderMasterID INNER JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure ON poDetail.BuyingUMID = MST_UnitOfMeasure.UnitOfMeasureID INNER JOIN ITM_Routing ON ITM_Routing.ProductID = parent.ProductID INNER JOIN ITM_BOM ON ITM_BOM.ProductID = parent.ProductID WHERE ITM_Routing.Type = 1 AND poMaster.CCNID = 1 AND Month(poMaster.OrderDate) = 07 AND Year(poMaster.OrderDate) = 2006 AND poMaster.PartyID = 94 AND ITM_BOM.ComponentID = 307 ORDER BY parent.Revision, parent.Code ASC
